{"tid":1202262,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"召集！居合，劍道，咩都好，12/6聯合演武 [裝備資訊]","createTime":"2019-06-11T08:37:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-24T09:33:09.000Z","uid":231905,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"491524e8dbf9dfb2ba5952e5e8aa2c6cd3033093","tid":1202262,"uid":231905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T08:37:39.000Z","msg":"鍾意居合同見到嘅朋友快啲嚟啦！我已經係當日港島區約好咗數以百計練習對手。佢哋嘅裝備包括：小圓盾，大方盾，伸縮棍同埋噴霧。<br />\n<br />\n想參加嘅朋友記得唔好戇鳩鳩去俾人打。頭盔等等必要野唔再講了。<br />\n1. 手掌同前臂嘅保護一定要做好，要擋住對手嘅棍，最多時候一定係用前臂擋。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BDJE10B.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBDJE10B.jpg&h=37ae7ac1&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/twsym0B.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ftwsym0B.jpg&h=d6d147aa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔夠裝備可以去呢個post，<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1202112/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1202112/page/1</a><br />\n又或者盡快買料自製，據前人經驗將膠墊綁喺手非常有效<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sJCa8Fp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsJCa8Fp.jpg&h=e839d0e2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n2. 我哋比賽係要贏，所以淨係檔唔攻擊一啲用都冇，對手仲會得寸進尺知你冇攻擊力就撳住你打，所以就算大家唔記得帶道具，都要盡量反擊渣啲嘢係手。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MVCym0J.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMVCym0J.jpg&h=7a75439f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n3. 今次比賽採達陣制，目的係要衝入目的地，所以退，遊擊，作用是不大的，該衝時求大家一鼓作氣<br />\n<br />\n分勝負係靠氣勢，有厚實嘅裝備保護，安全感強好多，自然氣勢都贏<br />\n今次香港人唔可以再輸，香港隊加油!"},{"pid":"0ac9f84a6e1cba58768d6585504ff8d8729f875b","tid":1202262,"uid":29663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T08:40:58.000Z","msg":"即使係比賽  上鏡都好緊要 因為有電視直播<br />\n所以要保養好皮膚  無時無刻敷住面膜係唔錯嘅選擇"},{"pid":"2394bb0d86afd5eff026eb8b5a74931f9b31d0e2","tid":1202262,"uid":133319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T08:42:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b16945f10bb0baf798151ea590f6f85ed5a7871c","tid":1202262,"uid":156375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T09:33:09.000Z","msg":"Push<br />\n最近都諗呢個問題<br />\n我地上完堂帶住木劍係好正常既事"}]}